data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!  Welcome to the established community of Central Park in Port Orange. With over 1900 square feet, this SINGLE STORY POOL home features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and provides a great outdoor oasis.  Upon entrance, you are greeted by the living room and dining room with a SPLIT-FLOOR PLAN. The Owner suite has a spacious walk-in closet, dual sinks and walk-in shower. The kitchen is in the center of the home opening to a breakfast nook and the family room where you can admire the beautiful screened pool and fully fenced backyard.  The family room has a fireplace to enjoy a quiet evening and entertain friends and family. Adjacent to the family room you have the additional 2 bedrooms, bath and interior laundry room leading to the 2-car garage.  Close to shopping, Restaurants  and a short drive to Ponce Inlet Beach.
